Potts, and can be viewed at                                           
http://www.TeamSpatula.com                                            
on the t-shirts page. Final artwork is now online for all current     
designs, as is all the ordering information.                          
                                                                      
I wanted to go ahead and start taking orders                          
now, as there isn't much time with this year's EveryBus being a couple
weeks earlier than in the past. I am placing the final order in 1     
week, so I need your order in my hand before then.                    
Ordering information is on the t-shirt page of                        
http://www.TeamSpatula.com                                            
If you have any questions, please e-mail me.                          
thanks!                                                               
                                                                      
